snippet: At Saturday night's Republican debate, the candidates with the simplest objectives tended to have the better performance.
abstract: At Saturday night's Republican debate, the candidates with the simplest objectives tended to have the better performance.
lead_paragraph: MANCHESTER, N.H. -- What you saw at the debate here at Saint Anselm College Saturday night was a set of candidates with differing strategic objectives. The candidates with the simplest objectives tended to have the better performance.

headline.main: Diverging Objectives in N.H. for G.O.P. Candidates
